><a href=\"/tc/terms?lang=en\"><span>Terms of Use</span></a></div><div class=\"columnContainer\"><a href=\"/tc/pics\"><span>個人資料收集聲明</span></a><a href=\"/tc/pics?lang=en\"><span>Personal Information Collection Statement</span></a></div><div class=\"columnContainer\"><a href=\"/tc/eu_privacy_overview\"><span>私隱聲明概覽 (歐盟)</span></a><a href=\"/tc/eu_privacy_overview?lang=en\"><span>Data Privacy Overview (EU)</span></a></div><div class=\"columnContainer\"><a href=\"/tc/eu_privacy_full\"><span>完整私隱聲明 (歐盟)</span></a><a href=\"/tc/eu_privacy_full?lang=en\"><span>Privacy Notice (EU)</span></a></div><div class=\"columnContainer\"><a href=\"/tc/cookies\"><span>Cookies 政策</span></a><a href=\"/tc/cookies?lang=en\"><span>Cookies Policy</span></a></div><div class=\"columnContainer\"><a href=\"/tc/code_of_ethics\"><span>準則及守則</span></a><a href=\"/tc/code_of_ethics?lang=en\"><span>Code of ethics</span></a></div><div class=\"columnContainer\"><a href=\"/tc/faq\"><span>常見問題</span></a><a href=\"/tc/faq?lang=en\"><span>FAQ</span></a></div></div><div class=\"copyrightContainer rowContainer\"><span>Copyright <!-- -->2023<!-- --> Television Broadcasts Limited</span></div></div></div></div></div></div><script id=\"__NEXT_DATA__\" type=\"application/json\">{\"props\":{\"pageProps\":{\"cateId\":\"local\",\"newsId\":[\"642ea1d813220566d11bd9c4\",\"港澳-政府研允建造業輸入外勞據悉擬不設人數上限及不經勞顧會審批\"],\"newsItems\":{\"id\":\"642ea1d813220566d11bd9c4\",\"title\":\"政府研允建造業輸入外勞 據悉擬不設人數上限及不經勞顧會審批\",\"title_tc\":\"政府研允建造業輸入外勞 據悉擬不設人數上限及不經勞顧會審批\",\"desc\":\"政府正研究建造業的輸入勞工計劃。據了解，當局初步傾向參考輸入院舍護理員做法，不設輸入人數上限，亦不用經勞顧會就每宗申請進行審批。\\n\\n本港不斷有大型工程上馬，但建造業人手持續短缺。建造業議會統計，去年有24.1萬名註冊半熟練及熟練技工，預測今年有1至1.5萬人短缺，到2027年更欠3.5萬至4萬人。近期最缺人手的是釘板、紮鐵、泥水等基本結構工種。\\n\\n行政長官李家超日前指，最遲年中會公布運輸及建造業人手策略，建造商會希望落實輸入外勞。\\n\\n香港建造商會執行總監梁敬國說：「我們會員很希望聘請本地工人，很坦白說，因為熟手、熟情況，但問題現在真的找不到人。未來每年有三千億工程，有北部都會區、交椅洲填海，工程量是多得很緊要，大家一定有工開，反而不夠人手的話，就算本地工友賺多了都很辛苦。」\\n\\n2018年本港曾引入518名外勞，到機場三跑從事填海工程。\\n\\n據了解，政府及建造業界正商討新計劃，初步傾向與輸入院舍護理員做法類近，即不設輸入人數上限，亦不用經勞顧會審批每宗申請，但維持外勞工資不可低於行業入息中位數，目前是23,900元。\\n\\n建造業總工會堅持反對輸入外勞，認為建造業議會可為工友提供培訓，令工友可以同時做多個工種。\\n\\n建造業總工會權益及投訴主任吳偉樑表示：「地盤裡運作，沒有一個工友能做到尾。譬如前面的基建，萬一未能承接，其慣常的工種，地盤剛到另一個工種而他又能做到，這可加長他在勞動市場壽命。」\\n\\n他又促請政府在規劃工程前，列明每個工種所需人數，讓本地勞工優先分配合適崗位。\",\"media\":{\"video\":{\"Can\":{\"sd\":{\"url\":\"https://inews-api.tvb.com/news/checkout/vod/sd/inews1/20230406/entries_642ea1d813220566d11bd9c4_46eb016dc5d1ddd918ce436c683c11f535188818_cht_proenv_854_480_800000.mp4\",\"bitrate\":\"500k\"},\"hd\":{\"url\":\"https://inews-api.tvb.com/news/checkout/vod/hd/inews1/20230406/entries_642ea1d813220566d11bd9c4_46eb016dc5d1ddd918ce436c683c11f535188818_cht_proenv_1280_720_1452000.mp4\",\"bitrate\":\"1500k\"}},\"Man\":{\"sd\":{\"url\":\"https://inews-api.tvb.com/news/checkout/vod/sd/inews1/20230406/entries_642ea1d813220566d11bd9c4_51c1264468e98475774dbe9a499d185f19543762_chs_proenv_854_480_800000.mp4\",\"bitrate\":\"500k\"},\"hd\":{\"url\":\"https://inews-api.tvb.com/news/checkout/vod/hd/inews1/20230406/entries_642ea1d813220566d11bd9c4_51c1264468e98475774dbe9a499d185f19543762_chs_proenv_1280_720_1452000.mp4\",\"bitrate\":\"1500k\"}}},\"image\":[{\"source\":\"entry_horizontal_642ea1d813220566d11bd9c4_1680778025761.jpg\",\"thumbnail\":\"https://img.tvb.com/inews_admin/pro/20230406/entry_horizontal_642ea1d813220566d11bd9c4_1680778025761_240x135.jpg\",\"medium\":\"https://img.tvb.com/inews_admin/pro/20230406/entry_horizontal_642ea1d813220566d11bd9c4_1680778025761_480x270.jpg\",\"big\":\"https://img.tvb.com/inews_admin/pro/20230406/entry_horizontal_642ea1d813220566d11bd9c4_1680778025761_640x360.jpg\",\"1200x630\":\"https://img.tvb.com/inews_admin/pro/20230406/entry_horizontal_642ea1d813220566d11bd9c4_1680778025761_1200x630.jpg\",\"link\":\"\",\"image_title\":\"\",\"default\":true},{\"source\":\"entries_horizontal_642ea1d813220566d11bd9c4_00001.jpg\",\"thumbnail\":\"https://img.tvb.com/inews_admin/pro/20230406/entries_horizontal_642ea1d813220566d11bd9c4_00001_1680778502975_240x135.jpg\",\"medium\":\"https://img.tvb.com/inews_admin/p